---lucky nine---

HAPPY NINTH MONTH MY BABYCAKES!!!! Thank so much for the past month!! It's been a very eventful month and I'm so lucky and hapoy that you're with me all throughout! ðŸ¥¹

Una, yung health scare ni mama na super stressful rin. I'm so lucky na you were always there for me during those times kase you really helped me become at peace during those times.

Pangalawa, my bday!! Yay!!! I'm really thankful for all your efforts, your gifts, your suprises, and everything else! You really really made me happy and its definitely the best birthday I've had in years. MWAAA I appreciate you so much and I'm so lucky I have a sweet bunion princess as my girlfriend!

Third, congrats on getting your job bby!!! Ang tagal natin hinintay to!!! And I'm so lucky na finally, you get to start soon! I'm so excited for you and I really think that you'll do great there!! And that you'll really grow career wise! Goodluck babycakes! I believe in you!!

Yun kang hehe, happy happy motmot ulit!!! I miss you so much and I love you so much!! MWAAA
